# plt

```text
usage: plt [-h] [-a]
```

Prints any symbols found in Procedure Linkage Table sections if any exist.
### Optional arguments

|Short|Long|Help|
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
|-h|--help|show this help message and exit|
|-a|--all-symbols|Print all symbols, not just those that end in @plt|
